# GitHub Linguist Configuration
# This file controls how GitHub detects languages in your repository

# Mark documentation as linguist-documentation (excluded from stats)
*.md linguist-documentation
docs/** linguist-documentation
README.md linguist-documentation

# Mark vendored/third-party code (excluded from stats)
vendor/** linguist-vendored
node_modules/** linguist-vendored
*.min.js linguist-vendored
*.d.ts linguist-vendored

# Explicitly exclude TypeScript files if they appear
*.ts linguist-vendored=false linguist-detectable=false
*.tsx linguist-vendored=false linguist-detectable=false
